& [ReviewedNarrativeAppendCliDesign] is the design contract for operator-facing reviewed narrative append
  @ [created_at] 2026-05-30T05:45:00Z
  @ [append_design] coordination/reviewed_narrative_append_design.sop
  @ [append_helper] src/negotiated_agent/narrative_append.py
  @ [narrative_surface] coordination/project_narrative_surface.sop

  + [design_status] is ready_for_implementation_slice
  + [authority_boundary] is reviewed_append_cli_not_freeform_review
  + [primary_goal] is load reviewed append evidence artifacts, build a result, and optionally apply append under an exact surface guard
  + [non_goal] is accepting ad hoc approval statuses from CLI flags
  + [non_goal] is generating Manager or Shaliach review evidence
  + [non_goal] is editing existing narrative entries
  + [non_goal] is advancing the work frontier

& [CliInputs] is the explicit artifact set the CLI must load
  + [required_ref] is NarrativeCoverageUpdateRecord artifact
  + [required_ref] is ManagerNarrativeAppendApproval artifact
  + [required_ref] is ShaliachNarrativeAppendClearance artifact
  + [required_ref] is project narrative surface
  + [required_value] is result_id
  + [required_value] is expected_surface_guard unless dry-run guard discovery is requested
  + [optional_ref] is result_out path
  + [authority_boundary] is artifact_loading_not_status_forgery
  = must: parse records from SOP artifacts rather than taking approval statuses as freeform CLI flags
  = must: reject output collisions for result artifacts
  = must: write a result artifact for both ready/applied and blocked outcomes
  = must: require an explicit apply flag before mutating the narrative surface

& [CliModes] is the safe operator surface
  + [mode] is plan_only
  + [mode] is apply_reviewed_append
  + [mode] is guard_discovery
  + [authority_boundary] is plan_mode_not_mutation
  = must: plan_only builds and writes NarrativeAppendResult without touching the narrative surface
  = must: apply_reviewed_append calls the guarded helper and writes the returned result
  = must: guard_discovery prints or writes the current narrative surface guard without appending

& [ParserRequirements] is the minimal SOP parsing boundary
  + [record] is NarrativeCoverageUpdateRecord
  + [record] is ManagerNarrativeAppendApproval
  + [record] is ShaliachNarrativeAppendClearance
  + [authority_boundary] is sop_parser_not_semantic_verifier
  = must: recover ids status fields refs counts and list fields needed by the helper
  = must: reject missing headers
  = must: preserve unknown findings and risks as strings

& [ResultArtifactRules] is how CLI output remains auditable
  + [default_out] is coordination/narrative_append_result.sop
  + [collision_rule] is reject_existing_result_artifact
  + [blocked_outcome] is written_without_mutation
  + [applied_outcome] is written_after_append
  + [authority_boundary] is result_artifact_not_frontier_advancement
  = must: include pre and post append guards
  = must: include Manager and Shaliach artifact refs
  = must: include blocked reasons for every rejection

& [ProofExpectations] is the minimum implementation proof for this design
  + [test_case] is CLI plan mode writes ready result without narrative mutation
  + [test_case] is CLI apply mode appends only when loaded artifacts allow append and guard matches
  + [test_case] is CLI apply mode writes blocked result and preserves file when guard is stale
  + [test_case] is CLI rejects result output collision
  + [test_case] is CLI rejects malformed or missing review artifact headers

& [ImplementationOrder] is the safe next split
  + [slice_1] is add SOP parsers for update record Manager approval and Shaliach clearance
  + [slice_2] is add reviewed append CLI plan mode
  + [slice_3] is add reviewed append CLI apply mode and wrapper
